barbell into the landmine device and load weight plates onto the other end. Stand perpendicular to the landmine, keep your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.</li><li>Grasp the end of the barbell with both hands. By keeping your arms straight and your core tight, rotate your trunk by pivoting on your back foot.</li><li>Make a little pause at the end of the rotation and rotate back to the starting position. When you end up a set for the one hand, switch sides, and execute the same movements on another side.</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Liquid" data-key="liquid" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1678783391829" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liquid" data-ver="1.1" data-id="1678783391829" data-name="Right click on this, and choose Edit Code."><div class="module gf_module- gf_module--lg gf_module--md gf_module--sm gf_module--xs {{extraClass}}"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tQOKCvLgGB4" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1684777203019" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1684777203019" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1657094583441" data-id="1657094583441"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1684777202971" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1684777202971"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 870px !important; height: 53.8333px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 435px 26.9167px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="